<P>THE BATTLE of HASTINGS, A TRAGEDY. By RICHARD CUMBERLAND, <ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> AS IT IS ACTED AT THE THEATRE-ROYAL IN DRURY-LANE.</P>
<P>LONDON. PRINTED FOR EDWARD AND CHARLES DILLY, IN THE POULTRY. MDCCLXXVIII. [PRICE ONE SHILLING AND SIXPENCE.]</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="dramatis personae">
<PB REF="2">
